flowchart LR
    A["Provider portal or secure operator input"] --> B{"Capture channel"}
    B -->|"Manual secure entry"| C["Checkpoint opened<br/>artifact capture suppressed"]
    B -->|"One-time reveal"| D["Copy once into governed vault path"]
    B -->|"API generated secret"| E["Ingest into namespace-scoped secret manager"]
    B -->|"Sandbox test user API"| F["Capture generated bundle into sandbox test-user namespace"]

    C --> G["Write only vault ref, lineage ref, and operator evidence"]
    D --> G
    E --> G
    F --> G

    G --> H["Create or update SecretVersion-compatible lineage"]
    H --> I{"Attestation passed?"}
    I -->|"No"| J["Fail closed<br/>quarantine run<br/>no activation"]
    I -->|"Yes"| K["ACTIVE or ready-for-cutover"]

    K --> L{"Rotation needed?"}
    L -->|"No"| M["Runtime consumes opaque ref only"]
    L -->|"Yes"| N["Issue new version"]
    N --> O["Update dependent refs"]
    O --> P["Verify cutover"]
    P --> Q["Attest cutover"]
    Q --> R["Retire old version"]

    R --> S["Historical read window if required"]
    M --> T["Audit and release evidence"]
    S --> T

    U["Forbidden sinks<br/>repo files<br/>logs<br/>screenshots<br/>traces<br/>CI stdout<br/>browser storage"] -.blocked.-> A
